it from something that you will use, go for the camp if you have the time and patience.  but there are some people who camp things for pharming purposes and this ruins it for the good guys who are there cus they need it.  they're the ones who create this camp animosity.  of course the other side of it is that laying claim on something that hasn't spawned is really annoying.  not all of us have a week to sit down and camp something.  it's not really fair for people to lay claim on something that will spawn 2 days later.  it's like those retards who claim a spawn in camp check when they've been sitting at the zone for 2 hours.  they &quot;intend&quot; to get down to the camp eventually....  this is about the time where i check my track or run down to the camp, if no one is there and there are no bodies and it's full spawn, you bet your ass i'm going to start killing things.  is this ffa?  i guess.  but i don't like making reservations to kill something in a game :P.  i understand why you camped lodi moon cus you're my friend and i know u and kay needed something from him.  and i think it's shitty for any guild to come up and try and take it when you're standing there at the mob.  i just wanted to bitch about camping <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uarryen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arryen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 630<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/24/02 3:17:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3085.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why do people think FFA is something more than blatent K</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Im sorry to burst your bubble but there are ALOT of FFA 50+ mobs.. Lod is one of the biggest.. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>I never understood this sort of statement.<br>FFA mobs aren't inherently FFA. They don't have &quot;KS ME!&quot; printed next to their name on the screen.<br>We decide who they are.<br><br>As far as I'm concerned, any mob which can be reasonably camped (and this includes Lodi, and the AC in SRo since you can run across that whole zone in about ten seconds), is not FFA. If someone else is sitting there waiting for it and you take it, you're either camp stealing or kill stealing (or both).<br><br>By all means steal my mobs and then tell me &quot;dood, its a FFA mob, every1 knows that!&quot;. Just don't expect me to have any more respect for you than I do for the wizards who used to gate into Perma and KS the named goblins my group had been camping for hours. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usagemonprayeth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sagemon Prayeth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 347<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/24/02 6:49:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3085.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why do people think FFA is something more than blatent K</span><hr size=1> Spawns like Lodizal are one of the things about EQ that really sucks.  How much bitterness and animosity has been generated by this one stupid turtle?  VS and the AC are the only other spawns in the game that have generated that much negativity.<br><br>Personally, I wish Verant would remove Lodizal from the game so that people from big guilds would go find something else to be petty about.  Or, even better, just make the damned turtle spawn right in the EC tunnel.<br><br>This mini-rant has nothing to do with you, Moonie.  You're a class act, and I hope you finally got your shield.  It's a shame you had to crawl around in the sewers to get it. <p>Sagemon Prayeth<BR>High Priest of Quellious the Tranquil<BR>A Twist of Fate</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalanonfadon>dalanon fadon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 118<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/24/02 7:28:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3085.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> lodi</span><hr size=1> i once spent a whole week in iceclad waiting on lodizal to spawn...did i sit there for 30hours straight? nah<br>I just got the spawn time down, as does everyone else that i know of.  Why do you think all those ppl showed up at the same time you were expecting lodi to spawn? they knew what time he was &quot;due&quot; to spawn. I personally respect anyone who is camping the turtle and would back off immediatly if he had the forces to kill the turtle when it spawned. and by forces i mean one shaman with malo and torpor and one warrior. This is not a hard mob to kill so most ppl dont bring that many ppl to camp it. If i show up with a whole group of ppl to kil this guy and there is a ranger there camping it....that doesnt mean hes got the rights to the turtle imo.<br>If i came to the AC camp and there was a level 20 char saying its camped...would i respect that? probably not.<br><br>If you have the forces capable of taking a mob down when it spawns right there at the camp, sure ill respect it.......if  you dont i probably wont. Keep in mind this is just my opinion on the subject.<br>dalanon <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap wi